'''Cormond''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal IV]]. It lay along the salt flats between the [[Suporro Sea]] and the [[Gravaal mountain range|Gravaal Mountains]]. Cormond's [[Trade Hall]] was the main center for the planet's commercial interests. It also contained the [[Cormond Museum of Arts]].

